# 013 — Persistence II: recent/autosave, undo/redo, export & report/material-library/design-history (Part I §I.5–I.8)

## Spec reference

- `C:\GitHub\Berreman\specs\0022\.spec-md` — parent spec (Spec 0022).
- Slice 003 (`.slices/003.slice-md`) — storage core: `serializeProject` with the shared `JsonSerializerOptions`, `StorageError`, schema validate-on-load, `.ocproj` read/write, `.binz` `Sidecar`.
- Slice 004 (`.slices/004.slice-md`) — `MaterialEntry` and the Part D §D.9 dispersion-model→tensor import mapping rules.
